ets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e21e16fe968e155f11167067d307e4fd4cc89d1","tid":2401121,"uid":8636,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T13:10:40.000Z","msg":"屌你老團支那狗"},{"pid":"e06d6dfca2264c57eebed901296de57d821e43a2","tid":2401121,"uid":58630,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T13:12:41.000Z","msg":"睇英文話 not the most likely喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;It seems to be ex&shy;tremely rare, and that be&shy;ing the source of the in&shy;fec&shy;tion seems to be ex&shy;tremely rare, and that&rsquo;s hap&shy;pen&shy;ing in a world where you&rsquo;re hav&shy;ing half a mil&shy;lion cases now every day,&rdquo; Dr. Ben Em&shy;barek said in a Jan. 31 in&shy;ter&shy;view. &ldquo;Trans&shy;pos&shy;ing that onto last year in Wuhan when the virus is not widely cir&shy;cu&shy;lat-ing in the world and think&shy;ing that could be the in&shy;tro&shy;duc&shy;tion is not the most likely scenario.&rdquo;"},{"pid":"b0d22a88d80150f54e856c460f58fec8f3f465e6","tid":2401121,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T14:10:54.000Z","msg":"笑到仆街<br />\n應該同軍人運動會有關"},{"pid":"02add7081fbcd56a5343a4ed9f3e53edf66048f4","tid":2401121,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T15:55:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BWCx7zJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBWCx7zJ.jpg&h=d5736e34&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c15c6c0fb93507d65f0f2a03eb5db1c4343e4572","tid":2401121,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T15:55:35.000Z","msg":"係美國"},{"pid":"86937db4475ba3e8a99b5546833a085e93116bf2","tid":2401121,"uid":226851,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0f5316b9ff3757070d98bc6a76fc8739f757310b","tid":2401121,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T13:05:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210209/SOYSAPXDQFGKJAWFRLOAZLUBTU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210209%2FSOYSAPXDQFGKJAWFRLOAZLUBTU%2F&d=%2BlEHcpGCWp7P1IX%2BOWqMQgjMvzJQG4GdM8cyRMJzdLg%3D&h=82021247\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210209%2FSOYSAPXDQFGKJAWFRLOAZLUBTU%2F&h=efba49fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210209/SOYSAPXDQFGKJAWFRLOAZLUBTU/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T15:56:28.000Z","msg":"新冠肺炎時間表 - 從病毒起源至武漢封城<br />\n<br />\n2015，美國實驗室成功將中國蝙蝠身上，類似SARS 但不具傳染人類能力的病毒改造，變成能傳染人類呼吸道的病毒，並發表在知名國際學術期刊《自然》。<a href=\"https://www.nature.com/articles/nm.3985?f\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nature.com%2Farticles%2Fnm.3985%3Ff&d=%2BlEHcpGCWp7P1IX%2BOWqMQgjMvzJQG4GdM8cyRMJzdLg%3D&h=b320c0a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nature.com/articles/nm.3985?f</a><br />\n<br />\n2019年8月，美國在Fort Detrick的軍事生化武器研究實驗室因恐防病毒洩漏而突然關閉.<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/americas/virus-biological-us-army-weapons-fort-detrick-leak-ebola-anthrax-smallpox-ricin-a9042641.html?fbclid=IwAR0QDlrtlbsk7gvhYqCYQtAefjOoZexMo5ADeI-IVpj2kfxQ2a_7o_682e8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.independent.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Famericas%2Fvirus-biological-us-army-weapons-fort-detrick-leak-ebola-anthrax-smallpox-ricin-a9042641.html%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0QDlrtlbsk7gvhYqCYQtAefjOoZexMo5ADeI-IVpj2kfxQ2a_7o_682e8&d=%2BlEHcpGCWp7P1IX%2BOWqMQgjMvzJQG4GdM8cyRMJzdLg%3D&h=714b7448\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/americas/virus-biological-us-army-weapons-fort-detrick-leak-ebola-anthrax-smallpox-ricin-a9042641.html?fbclid=IwAR0QDlrtlbsk7gvhYqCYQtAefjOoZexMo5ADeI-IVpj2kfxQ2a_7o_682e8</a><br />\n<br />\n2019年8月至9月初， 在美國各地發生400多宗不明肺炎， 美國疾控中心指肺炎或與吸食電子煙有關，但其他國家并沒有相似個案。<a href=\"https://www.statnews.com/2019/09/06/vaping-cases-rising-dont-know-cause/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.statnews.com%2F2019%2F09%2F06%2Fvaping-cases-rising-dont-know-cause%2F&d=%2BlEHcpGCWp7P1IX%2BOWqMQgjMvzJQG4GdM8cyRMJzdLg%3D&h=a29ed7e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.statnews.com/2019/09/06/vaping-cases-rising-dont-know-cause/</a><br />\n<br />\n2019年9月, 美國流感大爆發。<br />\n<br />\n2019年10月中，世界軍人運動會在中國武漢舉行，美國派出172人參賽，總成績0金3銀5銅, 排行第35。<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/2019_Military_World_Games\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F2019_Military_World_Games&d=%2BlEHcpGCWp7P1IX%2BOWqMQgjMvzJQG4GdM8cyRMJzdLg%3D&h=3440b81f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/2019_Military_World_Games</a><br />\n<br />\n2019年12月12日，武漢發現不明肺炎，一名69歲武漢華南海鮮市場男性商戶向醫院求診, 抗生素治療無效，肺炎原因不明。<a href=\"https://new.qq.com/rain/a/20200211A05AEA00\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnew.qq.com%2Frain%2Fa%2F20200211A05AEA00&d=%2BlEHcpGCWp7P1IX%2BOWqMQgjMvzJQG4GdM8cyRMJzdLg%3D&h=1b33c554\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://new.qq.com/rain/a/20200211A05AEA00</a><br />\n<br />\n2019年12月26日，武漢呼吸與重症醫學科醫生張繼先首次發現並上報此不明肺炎，並懷疑該病屬傳染病。 <a href=\"https://news.china.com/zw/news/13000776/20200209/37780703.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.china.com%2Fzw%2Fnews%2F13000776%2F20200209%2F37780703.html&d=%2BlEHcpGCWp7P1IX%2BOWqMQgjMvzJQG4GdM8cyRMJzdLg%3D&h=6764de86\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.china.com/zw/news/13000776/20200209/37780703.html</a><br />\n<br />\n2019年12月30日，李文亮、劉文、謝琳卡等醫生在内部微信群中披露了此次疫情相關的消息 &ndash; &ldquo;華南水果海鮮市場確診7例SARS。&rdquo; <a href=\"http://www.bjnews.com.cn/feature/2020/01/31/682076.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bjnews.com.cn%2Ffeature%2F2020%2F01%2F31%2F682076.html&d=%2BlEHcpGCWp7P1IX%2BOWqMQgjMvzJQG4GdM8cyRMJzdLg%3D&h=5f067444\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.bjnews.com.cn/feature/2020/01/31/682076.html</a><br />\n<br />\n2020年1月1日，武漢市江漢區市場監督管理局和衛生健康局聯合發出公告，决定對華南海鮮批發市場實行休市。<br />\n<br />\n1月5日，復旦大學在武漢檢測出一種新型SARS樣冠狀病毒，獲得病毒全基因組序列。<br />\n<br />\n2020年1月10號, 中國向WHO提交新型肺炎病毒全基因組序列, 並未發現人傳人證據，正追查傳染途徑。 <a href=\"https://www.who.int/csr/don/12-january-2020-novel-coronavirus-china/en/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.who.int%2Fcsr%2Fdon%2F12-january-2020-novel-coronavirus-china%2Fen%2F&d=%2BlEHcpGCWp7P1IX%2BOWqMQgjMvzJQG4GdM8cyRMJzdLg%3D&h=43ce3b57\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.who.int/csr/don/12-january-2020-novel-coronavirus-china/en/</a><br />\n<br />\n2020年1月20日，中國工程院院士鍾南山首次公開肯定存在人傳人，已有醫務人員感染，並呼籲民眾戴口罩及避免前往武漢。<br />\n<br />\n2020年1月23日，武漢市疫情防控指揮部發佈公告宣佈封城，自當日上午10時起全市公共交通停運。"},{"pid":"059da23869f08f48e15ef6434ac9051211ebd2fe","tid":2401121,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T16:06:20.000Z","msg":"會唔會係進口穿山甲？"}]}